<tr id="L66"><td><a href="#L66">66</a></td><td>WORF:  I have nothing to hide. Use whatever you wish.</td></tr>

<tr id="L67"><td><a href="#L67">67</a></td><td>CH'POK:  Commander Dax, are you familiar with a holosuite programme known as The Battle of Tong Vey?</td></tr>

